      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think I\u0027m surprised this section is needed. \"\"\"\"\"\" is not valid, and the docs say \"should not contain the initial quote character(s)\", which means the string s must start \\n and then optional whitespace. So I\u0027m not understanding why this section is needed. I\u0027m probably just being dumb...",
      "revId": "cedf9da073d4d11d9a62a16b5c3513771afce265",
